            <div class="card p-4">
                <h1 class="text-center text-primary mb-4">Human Resource Management System</h1>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <h4 class="section-title">Technology Stack</h4>
                    <p>ASP.NET, C#, HTML, CSS, Bootstrap, SQL Server</p>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <h4 class="section-title">Project Overview</h4>
                    <p>
                        I developed a comprehensive Human Resource Management System (HRMS) to streamline employee data
                        management, payroll, and performance tracking. This system optimizes HR operations, providing
                        businesses with a robust solution for effective workforce management.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <h4 class="section-title">Key Highlights</h4>
                    <ul class="list-group">
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>User Interface:</strong> Designed a responsive and intuitive front-end using HTML, CSS, and Bootstrap.
                            The interface ensures a seamless experience across devices, simplifying navigation for HR managers and employees.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Backend Development:</strong> Built with ASP.NET and C# for a modular, scalable, and maintainable structure,
                            ensuring efficient handling of core HR processes such as payroll, attendance, and leave management.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Database:</strong> SQL Server was employed to store employee records, attendance, payroll details, and performance reviews,
                            supporting efficient CRUD operations and secure data management.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <h4 class="section-title">Core Features</h4>
                    <ul class="list-group">
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Employee Registration:</strong> Allows HR to add, update, and manage employee profiles with detailed information such as personal details, job roles, and department assignments.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Attendance Management:</strong> Tracks employee attendance, working hours, and leaves in real time, providing detailed insights for payroll processing.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Payroll Processing:</strong> Automates salary calculations, tax deductions, and bonus distributions, ensuring accuracy and compliance.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Leave Management:</strong> Streamlines the process of applying, approving, and tracking leaves, integrating with attendance records for seamless operations.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Performance Evaluation:</strong> Enables HR managers to assess employee performance, record appraisals, and generate performance reports.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3">
                    <h4 class="section-title">Security Measures</h4>
                    <ul class="list-group">
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Role-Based Access Control:</strong> Implements secure authentication and authorization for administrators, HR managers, and employees, ensuring data confidentiality and restricted access.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Data Validation:</strong> Applies strict input validation to prevent vulnerabilities such as SQL injection and unauthorized access.
                        </li>
                        <li class="list-group-item">
                            <strong>Encrypted Data:</strong> Ensures sensitive employee and payroll data are encrypted to protect against breaches.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="mb-3">
